<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Lakshay Jain | Portfolio</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #020617);
      color: #e2e8f0;
    }
    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 80px 20px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #1e293b, #020617);
    }
    header h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    header p {
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #38bdf8;
    }
    nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 30px;
      padding: 15px;
      background: rgba(30,41,59,0.6);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
    }
    nav a {
      color: #e2e8f0;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }
    nav a:hover { color: #38bdf8; }
    section {
      padding: 60px 10%;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #38bdf8;
    }
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .card {
      background: #1e293b;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
    }
    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(56,189,248,0.3);
    }
    .tag {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 5px 5px 0 0;
      padding: 5px 10px;
      background: #0ea5e9;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px;
      background: #020617;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 15px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background: #38bdf8;
      color: #020617;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>Lakshay Jain</h1>
  <p>CS Student • Builder • Future Founder</p>
  <a href="#projects" class="btn">View My Work</a>
</header>

<nav>
  <a href="#about">About</a>
  <a href="#projects">Projects</a>
  <a href="#skills">Skills</a>
  <a href="#achievements">Achievements</a>
  <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav>

<section id="about">
  <h2>About Me</h2>
  <p>
    I'm a computer science student focused on building real-world solutions through code. 
    I'm deeply interested in startups, problem-solving, and creating impactful products.
  </p>
</section>

<section id="projects">
  <h2>Projects</h2>
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Shuttle Tracker</h3>
      <p>Real-time shuttle tracking system to improve transport efficiency.</p>
      <div class="tag">Python</div>
      <div class="tag">Web</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Future Startup Idea</h3>
      <p>Working on innovative solutions in fintech and automation.</p>
      <div class="tag">Startup</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="skills">
  <h2>Skills</h2>
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="card">Python</div>
    <div class="card">C Programming</div>
    <div class="card">Git & GitHub</div>
    <div class="card">Problem Solving</div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="achievements">
  <h2>Achievements & Courses</h2>
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Online Courses</h3>
      <p>Completed multiple courses on programming and development.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Academic Excellence</h3>
      <p>Strong performance in computer science subjects.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="contact">
  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>Email: your@email.com</p>
  <p>GitHub: github.com/yourusername</p>
  <p>LinkedIn: linkedin.com/in/yourprofile</p>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>© 2026 Lakshay Jain. Built with passion.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
